  <div class="wwf-phs-container  paragraph-container ">
  <div id="wwf-phs-id">
    <div class="wwf-phs-slide  grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="wwf-phs-content-left ">
        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>We're protecting our planet's iconic animals</h1>
          <p><p>We’re working to stabilise and&nbsp;increase populations of many of the world’s most iconic&nbsp;and threatened species</p>
</p>


          

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

     <div class="btn-wrap--item">
     <a href="https://support.wwf.org.uk/adopt-an-animal"  class="btn anchor_link  btn--white" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - https://support.wwf.org.uk/adopt-an-animal" ga-event-label=" We&#039;re protecting our planet&#039;s iconic animals  Adopt an animal">
         Adopt an animal
     </a>
     </div>

     
     
      
     </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="wwf-phs-content">
                  <div class="wwf-phs-content" style="background-image: url(https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/hero_m/public/2018-02/Medium_WW184614.jpg?h=297d9353&amp;itok=CJ_7L6oB);">
                        <div style="height: 3rem;" class="copyright--image">© Juergen Freund</div>
                      </div>
              </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    </div>

  <section id="wildlife" class="paragraph paragraph--text paragraph-container paragraph-101381">
  <div class="article_wrapper">
    
      <p>Here at WWF, we're working to increase and stabilise the populations of many of the world's most endangered and well-known animal species.</p>

<p>Discover how we're working to protect some of the planet's most iconic animals, from African elephants to bottlenose dolphins to giant pandas, by browsing our wide range of content below.</p>

<p>Simply click on 'read more' to learn about certain animals and how we're fighting for their survival on our wonderful planet.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

  </div>
</section>



    <div class="views-element-container"><section id="wwf_update_listing" class="media_panel">

